frus:attachment.p:
Koo-Pang; belongs to the boat; gets $2 per month as wages; is from Taiwanfoo;
                        has nothing on board, no goods; stopped at Hong-Kong below Pang Leoir;
                        arrived here eight days ago; bought wood from Kau-Soo-Moõe, a Canton man.
                        Moõe will sell wood at 5 cash one bundle; that is the price; three bundles
                        weigh about seven pounds. A true copy:
